oke('test')\r\n```\r\n3. Build with `pnpm tauri build --debug`\r\n4. Launch app, go to DevTools and check the Console\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nNo error\r\n\r\n### Platform and versions\r\n\r\n```text\r\n[✔] Environment\r\n    - OS: Windows 10.0.22621 X64\r\n    ✔ WebView2: 114.0.1823.58\r\n    ✔ MSVC: Visual Studio Community 2022\r\n    ✔ rustc: 1.70.0 (90c541806 2023-05-31)\r\n    ✔ Cargo: 1.70.0 (ec8a8a0ca 2023-04-25)\r\n    ✔ rustup: 1.26.0 (5af9b9484 2023-04-05)\r\n    ✔ Rust toolchain: stable-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc (default)\r\n    - node: 18.16.1\r\n    - pnpm: 8.6.3\r\n    - npm: 9.5.1\r\n\r\n[-] Packages\r\n    - tauri [RUST]: 2.0.0-alpha.10\r\n    - tauri-build [RUST]: 2.0.0-alpha.6\r\n    - wry [RUST]: 0.28.3\r\n    - tao [RUST]: 0.19.1\r\n    - @tauri-apps/api [NPM]: 2.0.0-alpha.5\r\n    - @tauri-apps/cli [NPM]: 2.0.0-alpha.10\r\n\r\n[-] App\r\n    - build-type: build\r\n    - CSP: unset\r\n    - distDir: ../dist\r\n    - devPath: http://localhost:1420/\r\n    - framework: Svelte\r\n    - bundler: Vite\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n### Stack trace\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\n_No response_","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/tauri-apps/tauri/issues/7301/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":1,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/tauri-apps/tauri/issues/7301/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}},"event":"cross-referenced"}]